<p>
I just bought myself a <a href="http://www.gameboyadvance.com/">Game Boy
Advance</a>!
<br>
(I know that the Japanese are generally bad at English,
but doesn't <i>anyone</i> at <a href="http://www.nintendo.com/">Nintendo</a>
realise that the name should have been the more proper &ldquo;Game Boy
Advanced&rdquo;?)
